        "subject": "LU-7111 misleading error message in mgs_write_log_param",
        "message": "LU-7111 misleading error message in mgs_write_log_param\n\nWrong params in tunefs.lustre might fail to mount targets.\nThis is expected but, the warning message is not appropriate.\n\nThis patch changes the warrning message to give an idea about\nthe problems it might cause.\n\nChange-Id: I6221b34cef2b62f5aa9aeb3c8b1abe0df08c135f\nSigned-off-by: Parinay Kondekar <parinay.kondekar@seagate.com>\nReviewed-on: http://es-gerrit.xyus.xyratex.com:8080/5915\nTested-by: Jenkins\nReviewed-by: Alexander Alexandr Boyko <alexander.boyko@seagate.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Zarochentsev <alexander.zarochentsev@seagate.com>\nTested-by: Elena V. Gryaznova <elena.gryaznova@seagate.com>\n"
      },
